        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Discounted Drugs for Clinical Trials Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows researchers to obtain certain high-cost drugs and biologics at discounted prices from manufacturers. Researchers must apply to the Food and Drug Administration for approval; manufacturers must sell the approved quantity of drugs to researchers at the discounted price and are subject to civil actions from researchers for noncompliance.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
